init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the â€œLost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You decide to go back in time to stop the drug from being invented.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You go back in time to the year 2029.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You decide to go to a university to find the scientist who invented the drug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You find the university and the scientist's lab.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You walk in and introduce yourself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You tell the scientist that you are from the future and that the drug he invented will have terrible side effects.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He still does not believe you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You realize that you have to do something drastic to convince him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You take out a piece of paper and write down the following:

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You will invent a drug that will stop the effects of aging.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This drug will be given to all citizens under the age of 26.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This will be done in the year 2029.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The side effects of this drug will be discovered in the year 2085.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The side effects will be so bad that society will be greatly hindered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is shocked that you have predicted the future with such accuracy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is also shocked that you have lost your entire culture to the drug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is convinced that you are a person from the future.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He decides to stop the drug from being invented.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He decides to destroy the lab and all of his research.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You walk out of the lab and you go back to your time.
